data.description: LIKE NEW! Beautifully crafted 4 bed, 3 bath home built in 2020. Boasting a spacious open floor plan with a variety of upgraded features both indoors & out. Stylish brand new LVP flooring throughout the main level & fresh paint! The kitchen is equipped with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances & plenty of extra cabinet space. With both a large bonus room & a separate home office, there is plenty of room to work or play. On the main level, you will also find a bedroom & full bath perfect for any guest. Upstairs, the sizable master suite features double vanities and his & her walk in closets. Laundry is also conveniently located on the upper level. The exterior of the home offers a large level lot and front & back covered patios. Liberty Creek Schools! VA ASSUMABLE LOAN!
